description: Used to switch DNA registers from LR to BP state. Expresses Bxb1 integrase and excisionase under the control of the pBAD promoter inducible by Arabinose. Regulated ColE1 ori (50-75 copies); Chloramphenicol resistance
shipped as: Purified Plasmid DNA, Stained with Cresol Red

description: Used to switch DNA registers from BP to LR state and back from LR to BP state using two different inducers (SR-latch). Expresses Bxb1 integrase only under the control of the pTET promoter inducible by Anhydrotetracycline (AtC). Expresses both Bxb1 integrase and excisionase under the control of the pBAD promoter inducible by Arabinose. Regulated ColE1 ori (50-75 copies); Chloramphenicol resistance.
shipped as: Purified Plasmid DNA, Stained with Cresol Red
